@startuml seq_slides_mirror_sync
title Slides Mirror Sync (Target Design, C2)

actor "Trainer" as Trainer
participant "Host Machine\n(PPTX sources + materials/slides)" as Host
participant "Slides Daemon\n(host)" as Daemon
participant "Workshop Backend\n(FastAPI)" as Backend
database "Backend Slides Storage\n(materials/slides on cloud)" as CloudSlides
participant "Participant UI" as PaxUI
actor "Participant" as Pax

== Change on Host ==

Trainer -> Host : Modify / add / remove .pptx
Daemon -> Host : Poll source catalog + mtimes
Daemon -> Host : Regenerate changed .pptx -> .pdf
Daemon -> Daemon : Build desired slides manifest

== Mirror Sync Host -> Backend ==

Daemon -> Backend : GET /api/slides/sync-index (auth)
Backend -> CloudSlides : List stored PDFs
Backend --> Daemon : current backend index

Daemon -> Daemon : Diff(host_manifest, backend_index)

loop for each new/updated PDF
  Daemon -> Backend : POST /api/slides/sync-file (auth, multipart)
  Backend -> CloudSlides : Upsert file + metadata
  Backend --> Daemon : 200 ok
end

loop for each removed PDF
  Daemon -> Backend : DELETE /api/slides/sync-file/{slug} (auth)
  Backend -> CloudSlides : Delete file by slug
  Backend --> Daemon : 200 ok
end

Daemon -> Backend : POST /api/quiz-status {slides:[...]} (auth)
Daemon -> Backend : POST /api/slides/current {url, slug,...} (auth)

== Participant Read Path ==

Pax -> PaxUI : Open Slides modal
PaxUI -> Backend : GET /api/slides
Backend -> CloudSlides : Read mirrored catalog
Backend --> PaxUI : slides[]

PaxUI -> Backend : GET /api/slides/file/{slug}
Backend -> CloudSlides : Read PDF bytes
Backend --> PaxUI : application/pdf
PaxUI -> Pax : Render PDF.js preview

note over Host, CloudSlides
  Backend storage mirrors host-generated PDFs.
  Delete on host propagates to backend.
end note

@enduml
